    "description": "加入众多系列中最受欢迎的Koa及其朋友Napopo的惊险刺激旅程，在Mara的世界中纵情探索！在这款致敬经典平台冒险的游戏中，穿越野生岛屿，避开隐蔽陷阱，击败最狡诈的海盗头目。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/7ff78c093ee9dcfe0a05847339010ef8.poster.avif?t=1768565195\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/7ff78c093ee9dcfe0a05847339010ef8.webm?t=1768565195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/7ff78c093ee9dcfe0a05847339010ef8.mp4?t=1768565195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>逐步揭开一个群岛的神秘面纱。从沙滩到沸腾的火山，这里从不缺少迷人而多彩的岛屿待人到访，每一个岛屿都充满了秘密和藏品。每个关卡都呈现出美丽视觉效果，细节丰富多彩，具有深度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/90ff0bf8c8c729d62b46367385ab4296.avif?t=1768565195\" width=600 height=225 /></span><br><br>放松身心，轻松一下——或者开始挑战自己！从新人到快跑侠，Koa和五个海盗（Koa and the Five Pirates）是一次适合所有人的海盗冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/6820e0722268e293c9fd1cb98cc6f781.poster.avif?t=1768565195\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/6820e0722268e293c9fd1cb98cc6f781.webm?t=1768565195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819450/extras/6820e0722268e293c9fd1cb98cc6f781.mp4?t=1768565195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
